<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #dc3545; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #dc3545; }
        .security-notice { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .reset-button { display: inline-block; background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
        .reset-link { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; margin: 20px 0; }
        .expiry-notice { background: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; color: #721c24; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üîê RMS Security</div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Password Reset Request</h2>
        
        <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
        
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your RMS account associated with <strong>{{email}}</strong>.</p>
        
        <div class="security-notice">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> If you did not request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
        </div>
        
        <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <div class="reset-link">{{resetUrl}}</div>
        
        <div class="expiry-notice">
            <strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This password reset link will expire in <strong>{{expiryHours}} hours</strong> ({{expiryTime}}) for security reasons.
        </div>
        
        <h3>For your security:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>This link can only be used once</li>
            <li>Make sure you're on the official RMS website before entering your new password</li>
            <li>Choose a strong password with at least 8 characters</li>
            <li>Don't share this email with anyone</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>If you're having trouble with the reset link, you can contact support or try the password reset process again.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>RMS Security Team</strong><br />
            This is an automated message - please do not reply to this email</p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px;">
                Request Details:<br />
                IP Address: {{requestIP}}<br />
                Time: {{requestTime}}<br />
                User Agent: {{userAgent}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
